OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781089372
OL,3,CAmputee hit by train supports new
OL,4,Csafety campaign
OL,6,FIt focuses on everyday behaviours that
OL,7,Fcan quickly become dangerous, such as
OL,8,Fusing a phone, wearing headphones,
OL,9,Frushing, or assuming it's safe because
OL,10,Fyou've crossed there many times before.
OL,12,FLucy says that when people do things
OL,13,Feveryday they can stop seeing the
OL,14,Frisks, "I'd say to young people, put
OL,15,Fthose mobile phones aside and focus on
OL,16,Fmaking sure you get safely across the
OL,17,Ftrack."
OL,19,FThe campaign aims to:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
